---
title: Double Balsamic-Glazed Beef Rump & Rainbow Slaw with Herby Potato Salad
description: Bring the summer vibes into your home, no matter what the weather is doing outside, with a potato salad and tender beef rump. There’s a balsamic glaze drizzled over the beef and even if outside is dreary, a vibrant rainbow slaw is sure to brighten things up.
